  <title translate="true">MODFLOW 6 Example: Define Quadtree Refinement</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1"><text styleclass="Heading1" translate="true">MODFLOW 6 Example: Define Quadtree Refinement</text></para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">The final step in our model will be to convert it to a </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="Discretization_with_Vertices_D" styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Discretization by vertices</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> grid and run the model again. We could have converted it earlier if we had wanted to. We will refine the grid around the multi-aquifer well and the stream.</text></para>
    <list id="2" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="%0:s." format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Select both the stream and multi-aquifer well and open them in the Object Properties dialog box. </text></li>
      <li styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Set the quadtree refinement to 2 click OK to close the dialog box.</text><br /><image src="Modflow6ExampleQuadtreeRefinement.bmp" scale="-99.90%" width="472" height="352" styleclass="Image Caption"><title translate="true">Quadtree Refinement</title><caption translate="true"><![CDATA[Quadtree Refinement]]></caption></image></li>
      <li styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Select "Grid|Switch to DISV and the DISV grid will be created.</text><br /><image src="Modflow6ExampleDisvGrid.bmp" scale="-99.90%" width="484" height="367" styleclass="Image Caption"><title translate="true">DISV grid</title><caption translate="true"><![CDATA[DISV grid]]></caption></image></li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
